HEADWORD: Flagship
<hw>Flag"ship`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>The vessel which carries the commanding officer of a fleet or
squadron and flies his distinctive flag or pennant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

